On page 3 of this thread, I presented a snippet and link to a source for the article by Thaine Reynolds &quot;Effective Specific Impulse of External Nuclear Pulse Rockets&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&gt;&gt; (I've already admitted that it's beyond my math </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->(the &quot;Effective Specific Impulse...&quot; article)<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>, but it does seem to be accepted by the engineering/physics community</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
